_sText:
The Ts have taken hostages on the top floor of the Cathedral.
Do the CTs have a prayer of rescuing them?
They will have to strike hard and fast!

This is a spinoff of the original cs_cathedral map posted here before.
This version takes place indoors only, to help improve FPS and smaller group playability.

I have removed the outdoors and the catacombs, covered the balcony and expanded some rooms.  You can still catch a glimpse of the graveyard...
